title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Sep 3 2022

description:
Liberal nepotism rolls on: MSNBC pundit Jeremy Bash, who cast doubt on Hunter Biden’s laptop, tapped for WH intelligence board. CNN lackey, James Clapper: It is assumed that all classified materials in Mar-a-Lago have been compromised. Top agent exits FBI amid charge of political bias undermining Hunter Biden probe. What does it mean when the FBI is interfering with our elections? Has Democrat Senator Mark Kelly of Arizona ever commented on the border invasion? Liberals will always put diversity and identity politics above merit. Republicans need to focus on three things: energy, crime, and the border.
